<para style="q1">

<verse number="38" style="v" />But you have refused and rejected;</para>

<para style="q1">you have been angry with your anointed king.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="39" style="v" />You have renounced the covenant of your servant.</para>

<para style="q1">You have desecrated his crown on the ground.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="40" style="v" />You have broken down all his walls.</para>

<para style="q1">You have ruined his strongholds.</para>
